title: DAZ3D - Exercise Room With Poses For Michael 7 And Victoria 7
description:
---Originally uploaded by ArgosDaz---

Exercise room with a barbells, dumbbells, chinup bars and pole - everything your characters need to become and stay fit - for use with Iray and 3Delight.

This set also includes 18 poses incl. 17 mirrored versions of them featuring lifting a barbell, exercises with dumbbells and a chinup bar for Michael 7 and Victoria 7.

With adjustments, these poses can also be used with other Genesis 3 Male(s) / Genesis 3 Female(s) characters.
